description: World of Warcraft progressive-level world with zones, quests, and spells.

1.0.0.description:
Initial release with barebones logic.  Includes:

- All races
- All classes (except Death Knight)
- Goals of level 10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 60, 70, 80
- Very important class spells are added early
- A YAML template file
- Lua scripts and Node.js bridge
1.0.0.title: Initial Release
